Package: spherstat
Type: Package
Title: Spatial point pattern analysis, geometry and trigometry for the sphere
Version: 1.4-3
Date: 2015-11-14
Author: Tom Lawrence
Depends: spatstat, globe 
Suggests: sphereplot
Maintainer: Tom Lawrence <tjlawrence@bigpond.com>
Description: Contains functions for the analysis of spatial point patterns on a sphere or a subset of a sphere.  Also contains functions for spherical geometry and trigonometry calculations.
License: GPL (>= 2.0)
LazyLoad: yes
ByteCompile: yes

